{
 "name": "RPlog_Simon_and_Jessalyn",
 "title": "Simon and Jessalyn",
 "summary": "In the moonlit clearing of Talon Karrde's base on Myrkr, the Telgossian Simon Sezirok meditates beneath the stars when the conflicted Jedi Jessalyn Valios emerges from the trees to speak with him about their future together. Simon confesses his love and, understanding the meaning of his vision at last, asks her to unite with him -- to share souls and forge a new order that would use the Force to heal the galaxy. Jessalyn, fearing she will become only a Jedi to him once they leave, is moved by his sincerity and admits she loves him too. The two embrace, exchange tender kisses, and as their passion deepens Simon asks that, if they cannot yet share their souls, they share this night, and Jessalyn draws him into the cover of the trees.",
